long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
TikBuddy is a comprehensive and premier Stats Toolkit for TikTok. With TikBuddy, you can view any TikToker Stats, TikTok video data by real-time,and track and compare any competitor, do objective analysis. Finally, TikBuddy will help you make growth on TikTok.

TikBuddy Toolkit Provide:
►Global creators score
►Global & Country Rank, last 30 days ranking trend
►Creators stats(includes Fans, Likes, Videos…)
►Videos stats(includes Views, Likes, Comments…)
►Videos music stats(includes users on the music…)
►Hashtag analysis
